data.name: ByDay_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of days of the week. Also it may indicate the nth occurrence of the specific day within a month. (MO,TU,1SA,-2SU)

data.name: ByHour_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of hours. (0,1,22,23)

data.name: ByMinute_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of minutes. (0,1,58,59)

data.name: ByMonth_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of months of the year (1,2,3,4,11,12)

data.name: ByMonthDay_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of days of the month. (1,2,30,31,-1,-2,-31)

data.name: BySecond_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of seconds. (0,1,58,59)

data.name: BySetPos_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of nth occurrences

data.name: ByWeekNumber_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of weeks of the year. Valid values are 1 to 53 or -53 to -1. (1,5,-2)

data.name: ByYearDay_description
data.value: Specifies a comma separated list of days of the year. (1,2,365,366,-1,-2,-366)

data.name: Count_description
data.value: Specifies how often the recurrence will be repeated. The start date counts as the first one

data.name: Interval_description
data.value: Specifies how often the recurrence rule repeats, null is equivalent to 1

data.name: Until_description
data.value: Recurrents ends at this date, including this date
